<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Features of NoteNestPro</title>
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap-icons/1.10.0/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    /* Additional custom styles (if needed) */
    .accordion-button {
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .accordion-body {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    .text-purple {
      color: purple;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container py-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 text-center text-primary mb-4">Features of NoteNestPro</h1>
    <p class="text-center text-muted mb-5">
      Discover the amazing features of NoteNestPro designed to make your note-taking and organization process easier than ever!
    </p>
    <div class="accordion accordion-flush shadow-lg rounded" id="featureAccordion">
      <!-- Feature 1: Easy Note Creation -->
      <div class="accordion-item border-bottom">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="feature1">
          <button class="accordion-button bg-light text-dark fw-bold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse1" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse1">
            <i class="bi bi-pencil-fill me-2 text-primary"></i>
            Easy Note Creation
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapse1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="feature1" data-bs-parent="#featureAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body bg-white text-secondary">
            Quickly create new notes with a user-friendly interface that allows you to write, edit, and organize your ideas seamlessly.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 2: Real-Time Sync Across Devices -->
      <div class="accordion-item border-bottom">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="feature2">
          <button class="accordion-button bg-light collapsed text-dark fw-bold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2">
            <i class="bi bi-cloud-sync me-2 text-primary"></i>
            Real-Time Sync Across Devices
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapse2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="feature2" data-bs-parent="#featureAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body bg-white text-secondary">
            Keep your notes synchronized in real time across all devices, so you can access them whenever and wherever you need them.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 3: Data Encryption and Security -->
      <div class="accordion-item border-bottom">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="feature3">
          <button class="accordion-button bg-light collapsed text-dark fw-bold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse3">
            <i class="bi bi-lock-fill me-2 text-primary"></i>
            Data Encryption and Security
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapse3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="feature3" data-bs-parent="#featureAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body bg-white text-secondary">
            Your notes are encrypted and securely stored, ensuring your data remains safe and private.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 4: Customizable Notes -->
      <div class="accordion-item border-bottom">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="feature4">
          <button class="accordion-button bg-light collapsed text-dark fw-bold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse4">
            <i class="bi bi-tags-fill me-2 text-primary"></i>
            Customizable Notes
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapse4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="feature4" data-bs-parent="#featureAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body bg-white text-secondary">
            Add custom tags, categories, and personalize the formatting of your notes to keep them organized the way you like.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 5: Advanced Search Functionality -->
      <div class="accordion-item border-bottom">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="feature5">
          <button class="accordion-button bg-light collapsed text-dark fw-bold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse5">
            <i class="bi bi-search me-2 text-primary"></i>
            Advanced Search Functionality
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapse5" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="feature5" data-bs-parent="#featureAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body bg-white text-secondary">
            Find your notes instantly with advanced search features that allow you to filter by tags, categories, and keywords.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 6: Easy Update and Edit Notes -->
      <div class="accordion-item border-bottom">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="feature6">
          <button class="accordion-button bg-light collapsed text-dark fw-bold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse6" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse6">
            <i class="bi bi-pencil me-2 text-primary"></i>
            Easy Update and Edit Notes
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapse6" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="feature6" data-bs-parent="#featureAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body bg-white text-secondary">
            Edit your notes at any time. You can easily update the content, title, tags, and formatting to keep your information current.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 7: Effortless Note Deletion -->
      <div class="accordion-item border-bottom">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="feature7">
          <button class="accordion-button bg-light collapsed text-dark fw-bold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse7" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse7">
            <i class="bi bi-trash-fill me-2 text-primary"></i>
            Effortless Note Deletion
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapse7" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="feature7" data-bs-parent="#featureAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body bg-white text-secondary">
            Deleting old or unnecessary notes is just as easy. With a few clicks, you can remove notes from your collection without any hassle.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 8: Best Feature - Smart Organization -->
      <div class="accordion-item border-bottom">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="feature8">
          <button class="accordion-button bg-light collapsed text-dark fw-bold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse8" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse8">
            <i class="bi bi-award me-2 text-primary"></i>
            Smart Organization
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="collapse8" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="feature8" data-bs-parent="#featureAccordion">
          <div class="accordion-body bg-white text-secondary">
            The Smart Organization feature intelligently categorizes and tags your notes based on their content. This feature learns over time, helping you stay organized with minimal effort.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
